            "description": "<div><p>2025-06-26股份回购统计名单</p><table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; text-align: center; background-color: #fff; color: #333; font-size: 12px;\"><tr><th style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0; width: 25%;\">名称代码</th><th style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0; width: 25%;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">回购股数</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">(万股)</span></th><th style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0; width: 25%;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">回购金额</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">(万元)</span></th></tr><tr><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">思派健康</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">(00314)</span></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">2.00</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">9.79</td></tr><tr><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">天安卓健</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">(00383)</span></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">2.50</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">2.03</td></tr><tr><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">旭日企业</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">(00393)</span></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">0.80</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">1.